Example 1
Let \(X\) have the following probability density function:
\[
f_X(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
2x & 0\le x \le 1 \\
0 & \mathrm{otherwise}
\end{array}
\right.
\]
Find the probability density function of \(Y=3X-1\)?

Example 2
Let \(X\) have the following probability density function:
\[
f_X(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
\frac{3}{2}x^2 + x & 0\le y \le 1 \\
0 & \mathrm{otherwise}
\end{array}
\right.
\]
Find the probability density function of \(Y=5-(X/2)\)?
